==English==

===Noun===
'''[[double]] [[star]]'''

#{{astronomy}} two stars that appear to be one with the [[naked eye]]; they either [[orbit]] each other ([[binary star]]s) or are a great distance apart, but just happen to be in the same direction ([[optical binaries]])

